com.gh.bmd.jrt.android.builder

Interface ServiceRoutineBuilder

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    InvocationServiceRoutineBuilder<INPUT,OUTPUT>, ObjectServiceRoutineBuilder

    public interface ServiceRoutineBuilder
    Interface defining a builder of routine whose invocation runs in a dedicated service.

    The local context of the invocations will be the specific service instance.

    Created by davide on 3/29/15.

      • dispatchingOn

        @Nonnull
ServiceRoutineBuilder dispatchingOn(@Nullable
                                          Looper looper)
        Sets the looper on which the results from the service are dispatched. A null value means that results will be dispatched on the main thread (as by default).
        Parameters:
        looper - the looper instance.
        Returns:
        this builder.
